Hamisa Mobetto has thanked her baby daddy for supporting her business. Hamisa runs Mobettostyles, a fashion company that dresses people. On her Instagram page, Hamisa wrote, "Thank you for your endless support. Ubarikiwe zaidi na Zaidi." Diamond, who during Zuchu's recent concert was dressed in a black suit with a touch of gold, said he was dressed by his baby mama, Hamisa. Speaking to Tanzanian media, Diamond said, "Nashukuru Mobettostyles ndio wamenivalisha. Ni designer na mimi kama Mtanzania nina kila haki ya kusupport Watanzinia wenzangu."